      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3165_0020-1"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><rs type="org" ref="#pmb29442">Frankfurter Zeitung</rs></hi></hi></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print">(<rs type="org" ref="#pmb29442"><foreign xml:lang="fra">Gazette de Francfort</foreign></rs>).</hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><foreign xml:lang="fra">Fondateur M. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb87771">L.
                                 Sonnemann</rs></foreign>.</hi></hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb182">Paris</rs></hi>, <date when="1895-03-07">7. März</date>.</seg></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print">Journal politique, financier,</hi></foreign></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print">commercial et littéraire.</hi></foreign></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Paraissant trois fois par jour.</hi></hi></foreign></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Bureau à <rs type="place" ref="#pmb182">Paris</rs>:</hi></hi></foreign></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb42671">24. Rue Feydeau</rs>.</hi></hi></foreign></seg><salute rend="center">Mein lieber Freund,</salute></opener><p>Ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ende <date when="1895-03-07">heut</date> ein paar <subst><del rend="strikethrough">Affichen</del><add place="above"><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02730-1"/><hi rend="latintype">Affichen</hi><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02730-1">französisch: Plakate</note></add></subst> an Dich ab, von bekannten <rs type="place" ref="#pmb182">Pari<c rendition="#langesS">s</c></rs>er
               Kün<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tlern: <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb92695">Chéret</rs></hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="latintype">etc</hi>, – die<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chön<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten, die ich kriegen konnte. Die<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>oll<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Du
               mit <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Richard</rs></hi> theilen, und Ihr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ollt Euch damit Euer Zimmer oder Vorzimmer dekoriren, wie
               dies hier die eleganten jungen Leute thun. Zwei davon – »<hi rend="latintype"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb92700">La Terre</rs></hi>« und »<hi rend="latintype"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb92698">Rose Croix</rs></hi>« –<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind in zwei Theilen; das wir<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Du übrigens<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>elb<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen. Grüß’ Dich
               Gott! Dein treuer</p><closer><signed>Paul Goldmann</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
